comment: Jordan (LAC) makes incidental contact with Walker (CHA) following the screen.
Batum (CHA) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
[Detectable with stop watch] Belinelli (CHA) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
Walker (CHA) intentionally kicks the ball on the play.
Jordan (LAC) extends his arm into Belinelli (CHA) to create space.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of LAC possession is overturned and CHA is awarded possession.
Kaminsky (CHA) sets the screen on Mbah a Moute (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The two players briefly engage and separate following the screen.
Redick (LAC) sets the screen on Williams (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Kaminsky (CHA) gives Crawford (LAC) room to land following the jump shot attempt and the contact is incidental.
Redick (LAC) makes contact with Kaminsky's (CHA) arm and body that affects his shot attempt.
Redick (LAC) makes marginal contact with Batum (CHA) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Redick (LAC) holds Walker (CHA) on the screen and affects his FOM.
Walker (CHA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Rivers (LAC) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] LATR shows that Griffin (LAC) makes contact with ball while it's still in the cylinder.
Jordan (LAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Batum (CHA) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.

Walker (CHA) makes contact with Crawford (LAC) that affects his SQBR.
Walker (CHA) makes incidental contact with Griffin (LAC) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Batum (CHA) is in a legal guarding position and blocks the shot attempt by Griffin (LAC).
Griffin (LAC) makes incidental contact with Kaminsky (CHA) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Kidd-Gilchrist (CHA) commits a take foul on Crawford (LAC).
Griffin (LAC) makes contact with Batum's (CHA) body and affects his SQBR.
